creator: Kreatos
descriptionHtml:
VIP in a snap!
Because you are so important to us, we proudly present you the Kreatos app!

Not only can you keep track of the last time you visited your favourite Kreatos salon, but thanks to the Kreatos app you can easily save for Kreatos Koins. You can exchange these for free products or a free treatment.
And that's not all, you also get a great present for your birthday!
Behind the virtual screens we keep working on new and especially handy gadgets to make your hairdressing experience even more pleasant.
Are you curious and do you want to be the first to be informed? Thanks to the Kreatos app you are always and everywhere up to date!
